{"tid":26871,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅軍集訓順便睇波　高普拉隊現身魯營球場","createTime":"2016-12-07T03:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T12:16:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd5b67cba31425a4dcae6d9c27028b6405c0934","tid":26871,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cew50v7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcew50v7.jpg&h=db739a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦周日在英超被般尼茅夫以4:3反勝後，隨即飛赴西班牙進行集訓，原來此行紅軍不但有操練，一隊成員周二更在完成操練後在領隊高路普帶領下到魯營球場欣賞了巴塞隆拿以4:0大勝慕遜加柏的歐聯分組賽，除了高路普之外，羅拔圖法明奴、占士米拿、拉爾拉拿、佐敦軒達臣、盧卡斯、米洛列特、奧歷治、韋拿杜姆等多人都有現身，可謂相當齊人。據報道，高路普認為球員暫時遠離英格蘭北部的寒冷天氣是有利，而紅軍將於周三回歸英格蘭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56014103&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56014103%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161207&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d7e5e4be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56014103%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161207&h=99a2fa1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56014103&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161207</a>"},{"pid":"319b82ad1309637a5bfca2da04355f7845d66c6e","tid":26871,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1096e2c46463cf01e7e556595fc41990832f23e5","tid":26871,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"工作於娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fr